         <abstract>
            <p>In this paper the principles of the laser speckles method is discussed and we used this method to measure the deformation of the gear teeth. In addition, the application of complex variables and energy method of theory of elasticity to calculate the gear tooth deformation has been improved. The measured values well coincide with the calculated results.</p>
